1. Set up virtual environment in the project folder using "py -3 -m venv venv"
2. Set up the python interpreter in VSCode "ctrl+shift+P" and passing the python path in the venv folder
3. Activate the venv by running activate.bat file in terminal
4. Install fast API in the venv
5. Go to main - initialize the fastapi 
6. Start the server using "uvicorn main:app" and check if the API is live
7. Use "uvicorn main:app --reload" to automatically reload the site when any changes are made
8. Path operation(route) - function to be executed 
9. 